COMMENTS: # File for working with Fairfax ingestion
# All lines starting with '#' are considered comments and ignored.
# The first non-comment line is used to extract column headers.
# ingest_status: pilot=PIL, standard=STA, standard_complex=STC, supplement=SUP, oneoff=ONE, technical_issues=TEC
# edition_discriminator: section_code used to discriminate between different editions
# section_codes: An ordered list of sections, separated by ‘,’ or ‘-’ or ‘+’, that couples all the sections in a publication
# processing_type: There can be only 1 processing type for a given row
# processing_rule: There can be multiple processing rules for a given row
# processing_option: There can be multiple processing options for a given row
# A single file can be grouped with multiple processing types
